text.tspan: NoBox uses a professional video encoder
to turn camera input into a live stream in real time .
No extra hardware, no complex setup.
Flexibility, stability, and top-tier image quality.
Network bonding is the core of reliable live streaming
Multiple internet links (cellular, Wi-Fi, Ethernet) are merged
If one drops, the others keep going - without interruption.
The stream goes straight to a cloud server - scalable,
ready to be received in a browser, player, or broadcast system.
